vd3d3LnpoaWh1LmNvbS90aGVhdGVyLzE1MTY48gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1690981859.45503", "card_id": "Q_615246429", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国顶级癌症研究机构称研发出一款「能杀死所有实体癌瘤的药物」，可信度如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "美国顶级癌症治疗和研究机构希望城市（City of Hope）国家医疗中心周二发布公告称，在临床前研究中，该机构科学家开发出一种能杀死所有实体恶性肿瘤（癌瘤）的靶向化疗药物。公告里所提及的临床前研究，已经以论文的形式发表在《细胞化学生物学》期刊上。前文提及的这款药物（AOH1996），是一款用来遏制肿瘤细胞增殖的口服小分子 PCNA（增殖细胞核抗原）抑制剂。根据临床实验前研究的报告，研究人员在 70 多个癌细胞系和几组正常细胞中测试了 AOH1996。这种研究性疗法阻止了带有损伤 DNA 的细胞在 G2/M 阶段分裂，并阻止了在 S 阶段复制错误的 DNA。最终结果的结果是，AOH1996 引发了癌细胞的死亡（或者叫凋亡），同时并没有中断健康干细胞的繁殖周期。美国顶级癌症研究机构：研发出一款能杀死所有实体癌瘤的药物"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "90 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/615246429"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iu5qup6W49YM3EAMaCDk5MDAxNDU0INa9qKYGMAA4REAPcgk2MTUyNDY0Mjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1690981859.48501", "card_id": "Q_597624922", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "贾宝玉反感「仕途经济」，为什么见到北静王恭敬谦卑，又接受「读书」的聆训?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e28a04d82bab19f0456f4d3e497fbb47_l.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "79 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/597624922"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iu5qup6W49YM3EAMaCDk1MDg2MTkzIM/GnKIGMAA4GUAQcgk1OTc2MjQ5MjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "